OL,3,CRoyal Marine who was awarded George
OL,4,CCross accused of spying in Dubai
OL,6,FA George Cross recipient honoured for
OL,7,Fhis service in Afghanistan has
OL,8,Freportedly been detained in Dubai
OL,9,Fafter being accused of spying.
OL,11,FMatt Croucher, who's from , was
OL,12,Farrested in the United Arab Emirates
OL,13,Fin November and had his passport
OL,14,Fseized.
OL,16,FThe former Royal Marine, aged 40, is
OL,17,Falso an Iraq veteran and won Britain's
OL,18,Fhighest honour for bravery for
OL,19,Fthrowing himself on an exploding
OL,20,Fgrenade to save his colleagues in 2008.
