OL,6,FRemarkably Mr Croucher survived the
OL,7,Fincident in Sangin, Afghanistan, after
OL,8,Fhis body armour repelled the force of
OL,9,Fthe blast.
OL,11,FUAE authorities charged him with
OL,12,Fintentionally and illegally accessing
OL,13,Fa telecommunications network in
OL,14,FNovember, and he was prevented from
OL,15,Fleaving the country, according to The
OL,16,FTimes.
