OL,3,CRoyal Marine who was awarded George
OL,4,CCross accused of spying in Dubai
OL,6,FNo further details about his arrest
OL,7,Fwere known. Now working as a security
OL,8,Fconsultant, he was forced to sleep on
OL,9,Fthe floor of an overcrowded prison,
OL,10,Fsurviving on a diet of chicken and
OL,11,Frice, his family told the newspaper.
OL,13,FHis relatives said they had been kept
OL,14,Fin the dark about his imprisonment,
OL,15,Fcausing them "immense stress", and
OL,16,Fsaid the allegations were "fabricated
OL,17,Fand absurd", the Mirror reports.
