OL,3,CRoyal Marine who was awarded George
OL,4,CCross accused of spying in Dubai
OL,6,FThey said in a statement: "We don't
OL,7,Funderstand why it's taking the Dubai
OL,8,Fauthorities so long to process this
OL,9,Fcase, a case we believe to be
OL,10,Ffabricated and absurd."
OL,12,FDubai officials reportedly obtained a
OL,13,Fwarrant for his accommodation in the
OL,14,FUAE, seizing an electronic device.
OL,16,FThe device was used for security
OL,17,Fpenetration testing as part of his day
OL,18,Fjob, a friend revealed.
