OL,6,FAfter being detained in jail for four
OL,7,Fdays, he was subsequently released but
OL,8,Fput under ongoing investigation, with
OL,9,Fhis passport and access to his bank
OL,10,Faccount seized.
OL,12,FMr Croucher was reportedly returning
OL,13,Fhome from work commitments in Qatar
OL,14,Fand Saudi Arabia in October and
OL,15,Fstopped in Dubai to catch up with
OL,16,Ffriends at the time of his arrest.
OL,18,FA spokesperson for the Foreign Office
OL,19,Fresponded: "We are supporting a
OL,20,FBritish man in the UAE and are in
OL,21,Fcontact with the local authorities".
